snippet.title: Blood of the Werewolf Opening
snippet.description:
Crossbow, claws, and courage. Classic monsters meet classic gameplay. 
Coming soon to Wii U, PSN, and PC. 

Play the demo now at http://www.BloodOfTheWerewolf.com

Selena played by Erin Cummings http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1423270/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1
